48
00:08:44,980 --> 00:08:49,840
As the ancients said, food and sex are the great desires of people.

49
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:53,679
Sui Zhi, there's no need to feel ashamed or concerned.

50
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:03,960
