Today's events were all done by Zi Shu on his own.

87
00:11:47,699 --> 00:11:52,579
Sui Zhi, you're like family to me. How could I suspect you?

88
00:11:52,579 --> 00:11:57,740
I believe that this matter wasn't ordered by my brother.

89
00:11:57,740 --> 00:12:02,380
