Prince Ning has left, and the play is over. Everything is okay now.

100
00:13:13,980 --> 00:13:18,340
When Liu Chang nearly searched the mansion before, I should've been on guard.

101
00:13:18,340 --> 00:13:21,599
I've pretended to be a playboy for too long, thinking it was flawless.

102
00:13:21,599 --> 00:13:24,959
Yet I never expected someone to come break my walls down.

103
00:13:25,819 --> 00:13:30,760
I underestimated Prince Ning's suspicion, I should've prepared a backup in advance.

104
00:13:32,159 --> 00:13:36,059
No one is a sage. How can anyone predict the enemy perfectly every time?

105
00:13:36,059 --> 00:13:39,100
Just be more careful in the future.

106
00:13:39,100 --> 00:13:41,620
The lives of countless people are tied to me.

107
00:13:41,620 --> 00:13:46,579
