108
00:13:46,579 --> 00:13:51,539
Even if I use my life as payback, it'd still be hard to atone.

109
00:13:51,539 --> 00:13:54,860
The burden of the empire is something you carry with me.

110
00:13:54,860 --> 00:13:58,880
You've given your utmost, so you shouldn't blame yourself.

111
00:14:01,519 --> 00:14:05,220
This matter is due to my lack of consideration.

112
00:14:05,220 --> 00:14:10,620
That's right, Your Majesty. Didn't we agree beforehand?

113
00:14:10,620 --> 00:14:15,279
If we're exposed, you immediately sever ties with me.

114
00:14:15,279 --> 00:14:20,140
Outside the secret room, you should've agreed with Prince Ning, not defend me.

115
00:14:20,140 --> 00:14:24,139
I did promise you. But when the moment came, how could I bear it?

116
00:14:24,139 --> 00:14:29,240
Precisely because we're like brothers, you should put righteousness above loyalty.

117
00:14:29,240 --> 00:14:33,319
If such danger arises again, Your Majesty must let go of me.

118
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:47,980
Third Young Master, for the peaceful world we seek,

119
00:14:47,980 --> 00:14:49,720
promise me.

120
00:15:05,819 --> 00:15:07,520
Sui Zhi.

121
00:15:10,750 --> 00:15:12,710
I promise you.

122
00:15:24,340 --> 00:15:28,020
A kingdom's business requires good advisors and heroes to accomplish things.

123
00:15:28,020 --> 00:15:31,620
Though a mere flower merchant, I'm driven by loyalty and righteousness.

124
00:15:31,620 --> 00:15:37,479
In the future, if I can be of any help,
I am willing to offer my full support.

125
00:15:41,440 --> 00:15:43,240
Mu Dan, please rise.

126
00:15:45,179 --> 00:15:50,059
Mu Dan, with your righteousness, Sui Zhi is lucky to have you.

127
00:15:50,879 --> 00:15:54,299
Meeting you is also a fortunate event for me.

128
00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:58,620
You and I are more than just ruler and subject.

129
00:15:58,620 --> 00:16:03,420
