133
00:16:41,819 --> 00:16:47,980
Whether I believe him doesn't matter. What I want are results.

134
00:16:48,639 --> 00:16:53,000
I was incompetent, couldn't catch Jiang Chang Yang's flaws.

135
00:16:53,779 --> 00:16:58,459
But with his nervous demeanor today, Jiang Residence must have secrets.

136
00:16:58,459 --> 00:17:01,380
How could I not notice?

137
00:17:03,579 --> 00:17:07,480
It's just several attempts revealed no flaws.

138
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:13,659
He'll surely be on guard, so be careful with future actions.

139
00:17:13,659 --> 00:17:17,619
If you can't hit the mark in one strike, you mustn't rush.

140
00:17:17,619 --> 00:17:20,319
Yes, I understand.

141
00:17:34,300 --> 00:17:36,780
This is the whip I use for interrogating people.

142
00:17:38,559 --> 00:17:43,040
Recently, through renovating, I learned many beautiful and cheap decoration methods.

143
00:17:43,040 --> 00:17:48,440
With this cunning merchant assisting you, I guarantee steady profits.

144
00:17:49,960 --> 00:17:55,140
Jiang Chang Yang, in the future, you don't need to pretend with me anymore.

145
00:17:56,279 --> 00:17:59,279
What I do is fraught with danger.

146
00:17:59,279 --> 00:18:04,459
You could peacefully run your small business, why get involved?

147
00:18:06,219 --> 00:18:09,419
A petty person seeks personal gain, a gentleman seeks the country's welfare.

148
00:18:09,419 --> 00:18:12,540
Though I'm a woman, I also have the heart to serve the country.

149
00:18:12,540 --> 00:18:16,340
Moreover, if corrupt officials are in power, people's livelihoods will deteriorate.

150
00:18:16,340 --> 00:18:20,319
What good days will we merchants have?

151
00:18:20,319 --> 00:18:25,480
I do these things not only for you, but also for myself.

152
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:30,140
Alright, don't put on a long face.

153
00:18:30,140 --> 00:18:35,939
Your sour look doesn't match the scenic wonderland I've set up for you.

154
00:18:38,340 --> 00:18:43,820
I haven't even asked yet, how did you pull it off in so little time?

155
00:19:06,900 --> 00:19:08,800
 Young Madam. 

156
00:19:09,540 --> 00:19:11,839
 You're also one of his people. 

157
00:19:12,440 --> 00:19:14,739
 Great, help me set this up. 

158
00:19:14,739 --> 00:19:18,420
 Set what up? I've moved all suspicious items away. 

159
00:19:19,559 --> 00:19:22,159
 Why are Jiang's people so foolish? 

160
00:19:22,159 --> 00:19:25,979
 If Prince Ning comes and sees nothing, he'll definitely become suspicious. 

161
00:19:25,979 --> 00:19:29,300
 After all, no one would bother to hide an empty house.  

162
00:19:29,300 --> 00:19:31,400
 Got it? 

163
