167
00:19:46,659 --> 00:19:48,380
 I'll take it away now. 

168
00:19:48,380 --> 00:19:52,019
 No need. It's useful, keep it. 

169
00:19:53,140 --> 00:19:54,919
Young Master.

170
00:19:54,919 --> 00:19:56,340
Where is She Yan?

171
00:19:56,340 --> 00:19:59,739
He was afraid of being scolded, so he flew away early.

172
00:19:59,739 --> 00:20:03,239
This happened suddenly, it was normal to miscalculate.

173
00:20:03,239 --> 00:20:05,580
However, today we owe it to She Yan.

174
00:20:05,580 --> 00:20:08,559
With him flying around, he saved me a lot of effort.

175
00:20:08,559 --> 00:20:13,620
If it were just me, I couldn't have set up all this before Liu Chang arrived.

176
00:20:14,419 --> 00:20:18,300
