182
00:20:38,860 --> 00:20:42,820
You two haven't forgotten such an important event, have you?

183
00:20:42,820 --> 00:20:45,839
No, how could we forget?

184
00:21:33,659 --> 00:21:36,000
Time does fly.

185
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:40,880
I wonder how many more years I can spend with you.

186
00:23:26,860 --> 00:23:29,219
At the New Year's Eve court session,

187
00:23:29,219 --> 00:23:35,620
