188
00:23:35,620 --> 00:23:38,039
Today is the Beginning of Spring feast.

189
00:23:38,039 --> 00:23:45,259
I specially invited you and your families to celebrate these glorious times!

190
00:23:45,259 --> 00:23:47,739
Thank you, Your Majesty, for your grace.

191
00:23:47,739 --> 00:23:52,039
I bow and pray for Tang dynasty's eternal prosperity.

192
00:23:52,039 --> 00:23:56,480
 Pray for Tang dynasty's eternal prosperity. 

