195
00:24:50,340 --> 00:24:54,739
Does Vice Minister Jiang think merchants don't deserve such noble items?

196
00:24:54,739 --> 00:24:57,800
You didn't send one for Young Madam to try?

197
00:24:58,428 --> 00:25:01,100
