201
00:25:10,580 --> 00:25:14,419
No matter how heavy the stench of money is, it's others who endure it.

202
00:25:14,419 --> 00:25:18,219
Once the courtyard gate is closed, living comfortably is most important.

203
00:25:18,219 --> 00:25:20,119
Don't you agree?

204
00:25:24,739 --> 00:25:26,939
Vice Minister Jiang.

205
00:25:26,939 --> 00:25:32,400
My wife's hands have always been for gardening and doing what she likes.

206
00:25:32,400 --> 00:25:36,259
These miscellaneous tasks have always been my responsibility.

207
00:25:38,739 --> 00:25:43,000
