00:26:37,759 --> 00:26:41,780
Your Majesty, the swordsmanship of the noble warriors is unparalleled.

211
00:26:41,780 --> 00:26:45,739
My younger daughter Ashina Dan has always wanted to seek instruction.

212
00:26:45,739 --> 00:26:48,919
I wonder if Your Majesty would consent.

213
00:26:55,359 --> 00:26:56,959
Please.

214
00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:21,600
Great!

215
00:27:30,239 --> 00:27:33,239
- Impressive. 
 - Good! Good!

216
00:27:33,239 --> 00:27:34,900
Well done.

217
00:27:41,620 --> 00:27:44,060
- Impressive.
- Nice.

218
00:27:44,720 --> 00:27:46,320
Nice.

219
00:27:48,820 --> 00:27:52,119
Everyone says Princess Ashina Dan is the steppe's Heavenly Maiden Flower.

220
00:27:52,119 --> 00:27:58,140
