235
00:29:03,819 --> 00:29:05,919
- Impressive.
 - Juebei Princess hit the target!

236
00:29:05,919 --> 00:29:08,279
Consort Shu hit the target!

237
00:29:11,419 --> 00:29:16,860
The spear and sword skills are evenly matched, even archery skills are too.

238
00:29:16,860 --> 00:29:18,979
When will we see a result?

239
00:29:18,979 --> 00:29:20,400
Indeed.

240
